<paragraph id="2DC3D05B135E713AA1D3FA6BC7FC38FA" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">
Italy. Puglia. Gravina di Leucaspide (Statte, Taranto) (WGS84: 
<geoCoordinate id="F4A29DD1CAEB391E2B1CB315D8153170" degrees="40.566319" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="1" value="40.56632">40.566319N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="5E79B01990D6BF7C78B902188B0C9354" degrees="17.190559" direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="1" value="17.19056">17.190559E</geoCoordinate>
), gariga, 150 m s.l.m., 25 June 2019, 
<emphasis id="D3B367A121B733E877DBD5EC0DAE0583" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">L. Bernardo &amp; G. Maiorca</emphasis>
(CLU).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="19EC4CE5A6E06B68E784555525C5E670" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" type="method">
<paragraph id="7FE542659F55F96C088C7BDD25109DEA" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">Method.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B3F22916B28E5ED14A1A414125C04D4" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">Squash preparations were made on root-tips obtained from germinating seeds. Root tips were pre-treated with 0.4% colchicine for 3 hours and then fixed in Carnoy fixative solution for 1 hour. After hydrolysis in HCl 1N at 60 °C, the tips were stained in leuco-basic fuchsine.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="A621D12DFB090D8A638E5DEE4DDAC20E" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" type="observations">
<paragraph id="E7BAFA537AE2AA09B4B5C1D243FEF0AD" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">Observations.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FF94DF0CD122FE8385C9695AC7676FCA" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">
<taxonomicName id="7E8EA47CC3FA8C64DECD895E753238A5" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Onobrychis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="subsp." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Onobrychis alba" order="Fabales" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="alba" subSpecies="echinata">Onobrychis alba subsp. echinata</taxonomicName>
is endemic to Southern Italy, where it occurs in Puglia, Basilicata, and Calabria. 
<bibRefCitation id="B0AAAB87FE598F7A6FFC9E05A6DEBCA9" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263500012331350395" author="Cenci, CA" journalOrPublisher="Plant Biosystems" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" pagination="91 - 98" refId="B4" refString="Cenci, CA, Bassi, G, Ferranti, F, Romano, B, 2000. Some morphometric, anatomical and biochemical characteristics of fruits and seeds of Onobrychis spp. in Italy. Plant Biosystems 134: 91 - 98" title="Some morphometric, anatomical and biochemical characteristics of fruits and seeds of Onobrychis spp. in Italy." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263500012331350395" volume="134" year="2000">Cenci et al. (2000)</bibRefCitation>
reported a chromosome number 2 
<emphasis id="3B052C597079202B8F0AD599A9CEF690" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">n</emphasis>
= 2 
<emphasis id="F88F845B2EC679236E256108D76244CE" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">x</emphasis>
= 14 for all the Italian subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="8D7BF3A679501DEB2C6CCE18B8E57D8C" genus="O." lsidName="O. alba" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis id="9ADD8089F7BEF3EB604F3126CFC3EB14" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">O. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but without providing any information about the source of these data. Therefore, we report here the first count safely attributable to a well-defined population of 
<taxonomicName id="313F5BD35FA8FFB18489A73FA1E5B6C5" genus="O." infraspecific-rank="subsp." lsidName="O. alba" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" rank="subSpecies" species="alba" subSpecies="echinata">O. alba subsp. echinata</taxonomicName>
. This count is, however, in accordance with 
<bibRefCitation id="F22441D52B16B816B34E71C0126123F7" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263500012331350395" author="Cenci, CA" journalOrPublisher="Plant Biosystems" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" pagination="91 - 98" refId="B4" refString="Cenci, CA, Bassi, G, Ferranti, F, Romano, B, 2000. Some morphometric, anatomical and biochemical characteristics of fruits and seeds of Onobrychis spp. in Italy. Plant Biosystems 134: 91 - 98" title="Some morphometric, anatomical and biochemical characteristics of fruits and seeds of Onobrychis spp. in Italy." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263500012331350395" volume="134" year="2000">Cenci et al. (2000)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="2CFA263C5B5AC3278633105AEB889930" author="Pedrotti, F" journalOrPublisher="Informatore Botanico Italiano" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" pagination="47 - 51" refId="B10" refString="Pedrotti, F, Cortini Pedrotti, C, 1971. Numeri Cromosomici per la Flora Italiana: 13-18. Informatore Botanico Italiano 3: 47 - 51" title="Numeri Cromosomici per la Flora Italiana: 13 - 18." volume="3" year="1971">Pedrotti and Cortini Pedrotti (1971)</bibRefCitation>
reported the same chromosome number for a population of 
<taxonomicName id="943F9EF6665D3B6BA36578EE6FB2E3E1" genus="O." infraspecific-rank="subsp." lsidName="O. alba" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" rank="subSpecies" species="alba" subSpecies="alba">O. alba subsp. alba</taxonomicName>
from Umbria. Our count supports the differentiation of this taxon from 
<taxonomicName id="AD945E33CF6B568427DE8BFFF9E1F779" genus="O." lsidName="O. calabrica" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" rank="species" species="calabrica">
<emphasis id="6A8005C1F08F20D52C7356FAC0D1005E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">O. calabrica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="E4A83509B4377DBC86EFCF1E4B32FEC1" originalValue="Širj">Sirj</normalizedToken>
., a tetraploid species with 2 
<emphasis id="A996F314E47EFF5BFADE72B11399E1DC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">n</emphasis>
= 4 
<emphasis id="8F4D9C69B51361FE31672903E0BD6DA8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">x</emphasis>
= 28 chromosomes, endemic to a small area in south-eastern Calabria (
<bibRefCitation id="7ECA55E1F62CB7A90BC5B93CFA833DB2" author="Bernardo, L" journalOrPublisher="Notiziario della Societa Botanica Italiana" pageId="0" pageNumber="117" pagination="71 - 72" refId="B3" refString="Bernardo, L, Maiorca, G, Franzoni, J, Roma-Marzio, F, Peruzzi, L, 2018. Dati preliminari su Onobrychiscalabrica (Fabaceae) specie endemica italiana misconosciuta. Notiziario della Societa Botanica Italiana 2: 71 - 72" title="Dati preliminari su Onobrychiscalabrica (Fabaceae) specie endemica italiana misconosciuta." volume="2" year="2018">Bernardo et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7FDFEF50F3A91E2AA5C66FB750D29058" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">G. Astuti, L. Bernardo</paragraph>
